Get Data from API and decode it

import base64
def convert_to_pdf():
  fread = open("E:\\Automation\\ABDALAZIZ-RPAChallenge\\base64Data.txt","r")
  b64 = fread.readline()
  fread.close()
  bytess = base64.b64decode(b64)
  f = open("E:\\Automation\\ABDALAZIZ-RPAChallenge\\file.pdf", "wb")
  f.write(bytess)
  f.close()
